<h2>About Blueprint</h2>
<p id="aboutP">Blueprint is an application created for contractors, their employees, and the clients who love their work.</p>
<h4>Contractors are able to:</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Create new projects</li>
    <li>View and change job information</li>
    <li>Keep track of employee hours</li>
    <li>Manage client information</li>
    <li>Send email invoices</li>
    <li>Compare profitability ratios for their completed jobs by viewing automatically generated graphs</li>
</ul>

<h4>Employees are able to:</h4>
<ul>
    <li>View job information and the tasks associated with those jobs</li>
    <li>Mark tasks as complete</li>
    <li>Check in and check out of jobs utilizing reliable geolocation and time stamping technology</li>
    <li>Get the weather for a specific job site</li>
</ul>
<h4>Clients are able to:</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Pay for work completed</li>
</ul>